text: Nimislyarovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Novokulevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 691 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 5 km from Novokulevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Nimislyarovo
